name: Team Anything: Dungeon of the Anything: Revelations
name_original: Team Anything: Dungeon of the Anything: Revelations
description:
So, turns out you're the Chosen One™. Big surprise. 

Now you have to fight the goblins! and my god there's so many of them, like, may as well be infinite. Good luck!

Coding - Rob Cole, Cesar Moreira, Cameron Mansfield 

Background Art - Mohammed Hussein

Enemy Sprites - Joshua Lofts

UI, Cover Art & Game Design - Gabriel Daka
